7750	/* =========================================================================
7751	 * Tool Call Text Memory.
7752	 * =========================================================================
7753	 *
7754	 * The model speaks DSML, while OpenAI and Anthropic clients round-trip tool
7755	 * calls as JSON.  Re-rendering that JSON is not always the same byte sequence:
7756	 * clients may preserve, sort, or rebuild object keys differently.  Tool call
7757	 * ids are the bridge between both worlds.  For every generated tool call we
7758	 * remember the exact DSML block sampled by the model under a random id.  When
7759	 * the client later sends the same id back in conversation history, we replay
7760	 * the sampled DSML verbatim and keep the KV cache aligned with the live model
7761	 * state.
7762	 */
