4456	     * or an explanation of the protocol.  Treating it as a real tool call
4457	     * duplicates it into both reasoning and structured tool_calls, and can make
4458	     * clients execute something the assistant had not actually emitted as its
4459	     * post-thinking action. */
4460	    if (require_thinking_closed) {
